snippet.title: God Eater 3 - PS4/PC - Story Trailer
snippet.description:
The fate of humanity rests in your hands. Break your chains, forge your destiny and rise above a world of desolation.
Watch the new story trailer of GOD EATER 3, coming on February 8, 2019 on PS4 and PC!
